{"tid":2385367,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"向BNO港人開放簽證申請為移居鋪路　英揆對政策自豪","createTime":"2021-01-29T03:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T04:00:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"df6319a69a0f5f68e28aff832c827a0244cdcb28","tid":2385367,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:58:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572977-20210129.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572977-20210129.htm&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w2lQkZRBUTTGMtnLt8L03NM%3D&h=8182d534\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572977-20210129.htm&h=e5c5a96b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572977-20210129.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n英國政府向持有英國國民海外護照BNO的港人，進一步開放申請簽證安排，為移居鋪路，首相約翰遜重申對這項政策感到自豪。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，履行了英國與港人之間的深厚歷史聯繫和友誼，捍衛英國和香港同樣珍視的自由和自治。<br />\n<br />\n合資格人士周日起可透過網上登記，2月23日開始部分人可利用手機程式提出申請。<br />\n<br />\n英國強調，有關措施是回應中國政府實施港區國安法，履行對香港人的歷史和道德承諾。"},{"pid":"b4d8b20e3d799372b3e2e715faccda6a4ecd8a2f","tid":2385367,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:00:42.000Z","msg":"根據對等原則，中國應該：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">開放5+1 CNO簽證比英國人申請, 最後移居入籍中國</span></span></strong>"}]}